      "q": "What order should I do Warframe quests in?",
      "a": "Follow the game's recommended-quest arrow — it matches the intended story order. The cinematic spine runs Vor's Prize → early lead-in quests → The Second Dream → The War Within → Chains of Harrow → The Sacrifice → The New War, then the newer chapters (Whispers in the Walls, The Lotus Eaters, 1999's The Hex and beyond). The one quest whose timing players debate is The Duviri Paradox — you can play it very early, but its story lands better later. See the full breakdown in the [Progression guide](/guides/progression)."
